ent-Z14ClothingHeadHelmetAborigine = Sphere-08 "Turtle" helmet
    .desc = Sphere-08 helmet used by Freedom fighters. Lighter than other Class 3 helmets, it trades some ballistic protection for limited psi-shielding. Modified with a Flecktarn pattern helmet cover.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14ClothingHeadHelmetBereza = Sfera-8 "Listok"
    .desc = A "Sfera-8" protective helmet, modified and reskinned in "Bereza" camouflage. Provides reliable protection of the head from bullets and shrapnel while maintaining its integrity. Equipped with a side flashlight for working in low-light conditions. Worn by use, but has not lost its level of protection.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14ClothingHeadHelmetBerill5MDolg = Sphere-08 "Tower" helmet
    .desc = Sphere-08 helmet used by Duty fighters. Lighter than other Class 3 helmets, it trades some ballistic protection for limited psi-shielding. Modified with a ballistic face mask.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14ClothingHeadHelmetBerill5MMilitary = Sphere-08 helmet
    .desc = Sphere-08 helmet used by the Ukrainian Military. Lighter than other Class 3 helmets, it trades some ballistic protection for limited psi-shielding. Modified with a small headlamp.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14ClothingHeadHelmetBerill5MMonolith = Sphere-08 helmet
    .desc = Sphere-08 helmet used by Monolith cultists. Lighter than other Class 3 helmets, it trades some ballistic protection for limited psi-shielding, which is unfortunately lost on its fanatical users.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14ClothingHeadHelmetBerill5MProject = modified "Sfera-08" helmet
    .desc = A modified version of the "Sfera-08" helmet with improved protective characteristics. Someone has painted it purple. It is the helmet from the "Beryl-5M". Armor class 3.
    .suffix = Z14

